<br>
Was in PoG a couple days before hand (druid in pog ??  yeah i know) <br>
So i die right... Pop at the Tree... ??  Bound at tree was stupid enough, but before the PoG Raid i was at work and figured I'd gate there and click in  <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
