So,  i died and went to turn around to walk away from the tree incase i clicked on it.  Well I used the mouse to turn...   = Dead.<br>
<br>
This happend just on sunday.<br>
I notice a sister guild in Kedge, raiding away.  So i go join em.  Somehow I get to be leading the group, i figure its cause im one of the highest peeps there and I have a map! hehe   So we've just killed Cauldronboil, sitting at the Crossroads.  We decide to do Esstrelle &lt;Sp?&gt;  So im nominated to tag pull with the other 54 druid.  <br>
Line of sight sux... i gotta get close.    I get a single (agro'd when trying to pull the closer one)  take back and kill, not too hard.  I get the other one and its clear.  Now i gotta pull some more of E's room.   I pull what I think is 2.   Get back to xroads.  After the warping/pathing catches up...  the cleric is dead, as is the chanter.  4 Mermaids, and Esstrella are dead (5 mobs) 2 groups, mainly tanks, only 1 chanter/cleric both dead!!!   <br>
<br>
Ok, we rez up. Wait for a couple LD's to come back.  We aree heading over to Undertow, not too hard,  invis over, kill a few easy mobs.  then prolly a couple horsies and then Undertow.  we'll we all 'vising up.  I was super strict on this, we were only moving if we were full mana/hps and ALL INVIS'ed!!  <br>
<br>
So we move out, along, up, down, around (im in front leading) Waltz straight into the mermaid room!!  LOADING please wait.<br>
<br>
Everyone, BUT ME, was invis!!  I forgot myself<br>
<br>
How bad is that!!!!      <p><center>
